  - Device frame (Section 8) — wraps mobile screenshots only
  - Limitations banner (Section 9) — for screenshot-only or wireframe fallback
  - Export footer (Section 10)
  - Scroll-sync controller (Section 11) — 4-state state machine JS
  - Print linearization (Section 12) — @media print token reassignment
  - Ethics compliance (Section 13) — MANDATORY in every report
  - Escape hatches (Section 14) — for edge cases only

  v3 REGRESSION SAFEGUARDS (check every report):
  - Ethics section present (Section 13)
  - Citation URLs clickable (rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank")
  - Screenshot panel sticky (position: sticky, align-self: flex-start)
  - No analysis logic changes (output formatting only)
